ByD Helper is tool for SAP ByD (Business By Design) Developers.

It will help you identify:
- the currently open view and show you the full path for it;
- the context of the last navigation;
- parameters of the last navigation, including the object UUID;
- inPort used in the last navigation;

This extension is related to my*.sapbydesign.com.
